His combination of technical knowledge and creativity led to many of the most successful projects we launched.

Ryan goes above and beyond in every area and Iâ€™m very grateful to have met him.

Ryan was also a key player in the early stages of our metaverse coordinator group. He had a diverse background to draw on, a deep understanding of cryptoâ€™s use cases, and an unstoppable drive to do good in the world.

Ryan did all the invisible work. When I first joined GitcoinDAO, he made me feel welcome. Later, he connected me to almost every important person during the Greatest LARP, including key partners and someone who donated generously to the fundraiser. He was a coordination superstar

Zoom meetings were often quiet until Ryan joined, bringing with him good vibes and order. He worked efficiently and helped us prioritize, collaborate, and stay organized so we could focus on building.
